properties.name: text
properties.value: Stopping to read any books you find is a good idea - they will contain important information about the world, or may even teach you new abilities. These first few books will explain the controls. Press 'W' to jump. Jumping while airbourne costs mana. Press 'Q' to close this book.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Ledge too high? Cast a teleport spell! Click and hold to charge the spell, and release to cast the spell. Remember, spell orbs are effected by gravity and you will teleport to the first place the orb touches.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Welcome to the training course. You will be guided through the abilities you have at your disposal to traverse the Monuments of the Old Gods. When you reach the end you will be granted full membership of the Guild of Explorers. Pull the lever to open the door and begin.

properties.name: text
properties.value: Multiple levers can effect the same platform in different ways. Some levers can also effect multiple platforms. Your path may be blocked until you activate the correct combination of levers.
